// (#331 L2a) A ref bound to a local from an UN-NAMEABLE source (an `if`/`match` value, not a bare
// handle name) has no single referent anchor the spine can prove outlives it → the Ref-storability
// gate REJECTS it (conservative over-reject) with the unchanged R5 diagnostic. Placed INSIDE a
// branch to also prove the gate DESCENDS into arm bodies (recursion fidelity). Compile-reject on
// both engines (EXPECT_COMPILE_FAIL).
use rn

(rn::bad(true, true, rn::mk(), rn::mk())) to i32
